  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM1.9">
<l>tūrāta maṉakkātaṟ ṟoṇṭar taṅkaḷ</l>
<l>kuḻāṅkuḻumit tiruppukaḻkaḷ palavum pāṭi</l>
<l>yārāta maṉakkaḷippō ṭaḻuta kaṇṇīr</l>
<l>maḻaicōra niṉainturuki yētti nāḷum</l>
<l>cīrārnta muḻavōcai paravai kāṭṭun</l>
<l>tiruvaraṅkat taravaṇaiyiṟ paḷḷi koḷḷum</l>
<l>pōrāḻi yammāṉaik kaṇṭu tuḷḷip</l>
<l>pūtalatti leṉṟukolō puraḷu nāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When is the day [I shall] roll on the ground jumping [for joy] at seeing</l>
<l>the Lord with the belligerent discus, who sleeps on the serpent-bed in Śrīraṅgam,</l>
<l rend="indent">where the sound of the drum filled with excellence reminds [one] of the ocean everyday,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] where throngs of servants, with inextinguishable love in [their] hearts,</l>
<l rend="indent">crowding [together] and singing many holy praises,</l>
<l rend="indent">melt thinking [of Him],</l>
<l rend="indent">- so that a shower of tears, shed with an insatiable delight of heart, falls -</l>
<l rend="indent">and extol [Him]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
